attributes.name: Title
attributes.value:
A scanning electron microscopy-based screen of leaves of Solanum lycopersicum cv. M82 x
Solanum pennellii ac. LA716 introgression lines provides a resource for identification of loci
involved in epidermal development in tomato.

attributes.name: Description
attributes.value: This submission contains cryo-SEM micrographs of S. lycopersicum x S. pennellii introgression line (IL) population. Ther terms "FEL" and "L" both refer to the first fully-expanded true leaf of the plants assayed.
